    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><em>You cover the bottom half of a rod of glass with a piece of fur and speak a word of power. As the fur begins to smoke, you yank the rod out of the fur and point it with a whip-like motion, a streak of lightning roaring out of the end of the rod as you do so.</em></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\">The lightning ignites flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried, which take [[/r 1d10]] fire damage every round until extinguished as an action.</p><ul><li><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 8d6 lightning]] damage.*</p></li><li><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span><strong style=\"font-weight:700\">*Upcasting</strong>: Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 lightning]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</span></p><p class=\"JDT-d xwmtH QGv3S DNLHv\" dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-f6jmp9907\"><span><em style=\"font-style:italic\">Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions.</em></span></p></div></div>",
            "chat": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Dexterity Save</strong></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\">The lightning ignites flammable objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried, which take [[/r 1d10]] fire damage every round until extinguished as an action.</p><ul><li><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 8d6 lightning]] damage.*</p></li><li><p class=\"MsoBodyText\"><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span><strong style=\"font-weight:700\">*Upcasting</strong>: Increase damage by [[/damage 1d6 lightning]]{1d6} for each spell level above 3rd.</span></p><p class=\"JDT-d xwmtH QGv3S DNLHv\" dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-f6jmp9907\"><span><em style=\"font-style:italic\">Some objects may be too large or flammable to be simply extinguished as an action, and will require creative solutions.</em></span></p></div></div></div>"
